extendedInfo.description: Gautam Buddh Technical University (GBTU) app is a free android app promoted by Fgrouptech and is Gautam Buddh Technical University (GBU) /(UPTU) located in C-22, Sector-62, Noida-201301, India. This app provide the web view of GBTU/UPTU website on the android products . This app is designed to provided applicants and student with all information related to location, courses offered, admission, etc.The GBTU/UPTU App has the following features (currently):1. Easy and fast access to the portal.2. Detailed information on courses offered and the free structure.3. Direct access to latest updates/results4. Download latest results/ notices on SD CardThis app is free to use and is compatible with android 2.3+ devices.
